OL,3,CHow does the UK prepare for floods and
OL,4,Cextreme weather?
OL,6,FStorm Bert has swept through the UK
OL,7,Fand left many communities reeling from
OL,8,Fthe damage it has caused.
OL,10,FSouth Wales saw some of the worst
OL,11,Fflooding in the country and it has
OL,12,Fleft many asking if more could have
OL,13,Fbeen done to prevent it.
OL,15,FPontypridd and nearby areas were put
OL,16,Funder water on Sunday and Monday, with
OL,17,Fmany residents amazed only a yellow
OL,18,Fweather warning was issued for the
OL,19,Fregion in the days prior.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
