OL,3,CHow does the UK prepare for floods and
OL,4,Cextreme weather?
OL,6,FPeople also reacted with anger about
OL,7,Fhow Natural Resources Wales (NRW)
OL,8,Fmanages flood risk in the country.
OL,10,FJohn Morgan, manager of the Rheola pub
OL,11,Fin Porth, said he had been flooded
OL,12,Fthree times in four years.
OL,14,FHe said: "What good are warnings at
OL,15,Fthree o'clock in the morning, they are
OL,16,Fno good.
OL,18,F"What needs to be done is the
OL,19,Fdefences, dredge the rivers, build
OL,20,Fwalls."
