OL,3,CHow does the UK prepare for floods and
OL,4,Cextreme weather?
OL,6,FNRW said it had issued flood warnings
OL,7,Fbefore the downpour but there was "no
OL,8,Fsilver bullet" to managing the flood
OL,9,Frisk in the area around the River Taff.
OL,11,FSally Davies, duty tactical manager
OL,12,FWales at NRW, said: "Our teams worked
OL,13,Faround the clock, working with
OL,14,Femergency services to respond to this
OL,15,Fsignificant incident. As we do with
OL,16,Fevery significant flood event, we will
OL,17,Fnow review the response as we enter
OL,18,Fthe recovery phase."
