OL,3,CHow does the UK prepare for floods and
OL,4,Cextreme weather?
OL,6,FEvery time the UK experiences flooding
OL,7,Fpeople always ask if things could have
OL,8,Fbeen done differently, but just how
OL,9,Fdoes Britain prepare for extreme
OL,10,Fweather?
OL,12,FWhat warning systems do we have?
OL,14,FThe UK relies on two different systems
OL,15,Fto predict the impact of severe
OL,16,Fweather.
OL,18,FFor the weather as a whole, the Met
OL,19,FOffice issues weather warnings under a
OL,20,Fred, amber, yellow system.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
