OL,3,CHow does the UK prepare for floods and
OL,4,Cextreme weather?
OL,6,FThis covers all weather events from
OL,7,Fheatwaves to blizzards.
OL,9,FFor specifically floods the
OL,10,Fenvironmental agencies of England,
OL,11,FScotland and Wales issue flood
OL,12,Fwarnings in response to predicted
OL,13,Fsevere weather.
OL,15,FThe flood warnings are issued as
OL,16,Feither 'alerts', 'warnings', or
OL,17,F'severe warnings'.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
