OL,3,CHow does the UK prepare for floods and
OL,4,Cextreme weather?
OL,6,FAn alert indicates flooding is
OL,7,Fpossible, a warning indicates flooding
OL,8,Fis expected and a severe warning
OL,9,Findicates flooding is expected and
OL,10,Fthere could be a risk to life.
OL,12,FHow frequent are red warnings?
OL,14,FThe red weather warnings are extremely
OL,15,Frare, some years will go without
OL,16,Fhaving any.
OL,18,FA red warning means danger to life is
OL,19,Fexpected and anyone in the impacted
OL,20,Farea should take precautions and avoid
OL,21,Ftravelling.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
