OL,3,CHow does the UK prepare for floods and
OL,4,Cextreme weather?
OL,6,FSubstantial disruption to travel and
OL,7,Fenergy supplies is also expected.
OL,9,FThe last time a red weather warning
OL,10,Fwas issued was in October 2023 for
OL,11,FStorm Babet across northern Scotland.
OL,13,FTwo people were killed and hundreds of
OL,14,Fhomes were evacuated.
OL,16,FSimilarly, severe flood warnings are
OL,17,Falso rare, during instances of heavy
OL,18,Frain across the country the
OL,19,Fenvironment agencies may issue
OL,20,Fhundreds of flood alerts but just one
OL,21,For two severe warnings.
