OL,3,CHow does the UK prepare for floods and
OL,4,Cextreme weather?
OL,6,FHow common is extreme weather?
OL,8,FThe UK's mild climate means extreme
OL,9,Fweather is not very likely, but the
OL,10,FMet Office has warned this may change
OL,11,Fas a result of climate change.
OL,13,FIn 2023, the Met Office compared
OL,14,Fweather data and events from last year
OL,15,Fwith statistics dating back to the
OL,16,F19th century.
OL,18,FThe report flagged two key trends, the
OL,19,Fnumber of "hot" days (28C or above)
OL,20,Fand "extremely wet" days are both
OL,21,Fincreasing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
