OL,3,CHow does the UK prepare for floods and
OL,4,Cextreme weather?
OL,6,FExtreme weather is notoriously hard to
OL,7,Fpredict outside of a few weeks into
OL,8,Fthe future, so even with trends
OL,9,Fappearing to show they are more
OL,10,Fcommon, the UK could still go years
OL,11,Fwithout one, or experience multiple in
OL,12,Fa single season.
OL,14,FHow do we prepare for floods?
OL,16,FRecent governments have had a mixed
OL,17,Frecord when it comes to protecting the
OL,18,Fcountry against floods.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
