OL,3,CHow does the UK prepare for floods and
OL,4,Cextreme weather?
OL,6,FThe UK has numerous flood defences
OL,7,Fdotted around the country aimed at
OL,8,Fprotecting particularly vulnerable
OL,9,Fareas, with more than 75,000 defences
OL,10,Fin England alone.
OL,12,FBut a report by the Public Accounts
OL,13,FCommittee in January 2024 found the UK
OL,14,Fhad not kept its defences well
OL,15,Fmaintained and it could lead to more
OL,16,Fflooding.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
