OL,3,CHow does the UK prepare for floods and
OL,4,Cextreme weather?
OL,6,FThey found due to the lack of defences
OL,7,Fcaused by poor management and longer
OL,8,Fthan expected delivery times 40% fewer
OL,9,Fproperties would be protected during a
OL,10,Fflood than the government's own
OL,11,Ffigures expect.
OL,13,FThe report said 5.7 million properties
OL,14,Fin England were at risk of flooding in
OL,15,F2023 and despite a government plan to
OL,16,Freduce this to 5.5 million by 2027,
OL,17,Fthe figure is likely to increase.
OL,19,FThey said this was due to poor
OL,20,Fmaintenance of current defences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
