OL,3,CHow does the UK prepare for floods and
OL,4,Cextreme weather?
OL,6,FLocal authorities also keep on
OL,7,Fapproving more buildings on high-risk
OL,8,Fflood plains.
OL,10,FIn October 2024 the think-tank Localis
OL,11,Freported that 7,000 homes were
OL,12,Fapproved in areas like King's Lynn and
OL,13,FWest Norfolk - regions considered some
OL,14,Fof the most prone to flooding in
OL,15,FEngland.
OL,17,FDespite this, the government is
OL,18,Fspending billions more on further
OL,19,Fflood defences, doubling capital
OL,20,Fspending in March 2020 to #5.2bn.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
