OL,3,CHow does the UK prepare for floods and
OL,4,Cextreme weather?
OL,6,FLabour also committed #2.4bn for flood
OL,7,Fdefences in its first budget after
OL,8,Fentering power.
OL,10,FThe Labour government also announced
OL,11,Freforms on how flood planning would be
OL,12,Forganised aimed at supporting rural
OL,13,Fcommunities and farms by introducing
OL,14,Fbetter draining and looking at
OL,15,Falternative ways to prevent floods.
OL,17,FThe Met Office is also considered one
OL,18,Fof the best meteorological
OL,19,Forganisations in the world and has a
OL,20,Fstrong reputation for predicting
OL,21,Fextreme weather as quickly as possible.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
